sequenceDiagram
    participant CA as Confidence Analyst
    participant CT as Confidence Tuner
    participant CV as Confidence Validator
    participant KG as Knowledge Graph
    participant RE as Research Engine

    Note over CA,RE: Confidence Tuning Cycle

    RE->>CA: Send Research Results
    activate CA
    CA->>KG: Analyze Current Patterns
    KG-->>CA: Pattern Statistics
    CA->>CA: Calculate Metrics
    CA-->>CT: Suggest Parameter Updates
    deactivate CA

    activate CT
    CT->>CT: Generate Adjustments
    CT->>CV: Request Validation
    deactivate CT

    activate CV
    CV->>KG: Check Historical Data
    KG-->>CV: Performance History
    CV->>CV: Validate Changes
    CV-->>RE: Approved Updates
    deactivate CV

    RE->>KG: Apply New Parameters
    KG-->>RE: Confirmation

    Note over CA,RE: Learning Feedback

    loop Continuous Learning
        RE->>KG: Store Results
        KG->>CA: Update Metrics
        CA->>CT: Fine-tune Parameters
        CT->>CV: Validate Changes
        CV-->>RE: Apply Updates
    end

    Note over CA,RE: Cross-Domain Adaptation

    par Domain Specific Learning
        CA->>KG: Analyze Domain Patterns
        KG-->>CA: Domain Statistics
        CA->>CT: Domain Adjustments
    and Global Learning
        CA->>KG: Analyze Global Patterns
        KG-->>CA: Global Statistics
        CA->>CT: Global Adjustments
    end

    CT->>CV: Merge Adjustments
    CV-->>RE: Apply Combined Updates